        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"546447\">@Benno Lossin</span> <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"671004\">@Danilo Krummrich</span> I need an array of locks. The size of the array is configurable from user input, but remains constant after construction. Is there a safe way to construct a <code>Pin&lt;KVec&lt;SpinLock&lt;_&gt;&gt;&gt;</code> or a <code>Pin&lt;&amp;[SpinLock]&gt;</code>?</p>",
